text: San Stefano Grand Plaza San Stefano Grand Plaza during the final preparations for opening, 2006 San Stefano Grand Plaza () is a structural complex including apartments, offices, a shopping mall and a marina in Alexandria, Egypt. It was designed by WZMH Architects. == See also == * List of shopping malls in Egypt ==References== ==External links== Category:Hotels in Alexandria Category:Shopping malls in Egypt Category:WZMH Architects buildings Category:Buildings and structures in Alexandria
